    "description": {
      "chat": "",
      "gmnotes": "",
      "short": "",
      "unidentified": "",
      "value": "<p>Due to her conditioning, an orc can choose one skill that becomes a class skill for her. If the chosen skill is a class skill from the class she takes at 1st level, she instead gains a +1 bonus to checks with that skill. In addition, due to her confidence with that skill, once per day, before she attempts a check with the chosen skill, the orc can grant herself a +2 bonus to that check.</p>\n<p><em>Once per day usage is tracked with @UUID[Compendium.sfrpg.racial-features.XL2cWvY1VPsP7WOo]{Conditioned Focus (+2 Focus)}. Edit the modifiers with the chosen skill in the Modifier tabs of both feature items.</em></p>"
